To build and install cngpijmon:

        for rpm
        ./autogen.sh --datadir=/usr/local/share --program-suffix=<Printer Model Name> --enable-progpath=<cnijnpr Program Path>
        for deb
        ./autogen.sh --prefix=/usr --program-suffix=<Printer Model Name> --enable-progpath=<cnijnpr Program Path> --datadir=/usr/share
        
        make
        make install

To build and install cngpijmon with AUTOCONF

You can set the following <Printer Model Name>.
            e600
            mx370
            mx430
            mx510
            mx710
            mx890
            ip100
            
You can set the following <cnijnpr Program Path>.
            /usr/local/bin
            /usr/bin


Example for building the mx890 cngpijmon with the new automake and autoconf:
        for rpm
        ./autogen.sh --datadir=/usr/local/share --program-suffix=mx890 --enable-progpath=/usr/local/bin
        for deb
        ./autogen.sh --prefix=/usr --program-suffix=mx890 --enable-progpath=/usr/bin --datadir=/usr/share
        
        make
        make install

